{"tid":1079540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲少女嚐禁果！汽旅內「麻花式交纏」　LINE一句「會痛」28歲男友臉綠了","createTime":"2019-03-27T04:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T06:47:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c10844b71fb0bf0caa9701afb1b42a2607282f1e","tid":1079540,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:22:33.000Z","msg":"一名28歲鄭姓美髮師任職於母親經營的美容院，並與母親所雇用的12歲少女交往，還曾赴汽車旅館發生關係。少女家人得知她交男友後，便查看其手機，竟意外在LINE訊息中看見「插進去的時候會痛。」驚覺2人偷嚐禁果，憤而報警。<span style=\"color: red;\">新北</span>地院依與未滿14歲性交罪，將鄭男判處3年6個月有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報導，鄭男在母親經營的美容院擔任美髮師，2018年間母親雇用剛滿12歲的少女，2人進而交往。同年3月鄭男騎機車載對方外出遊玩，竟藉故把少女帶到汽車旅館開房間。<br />\n<br />\n少女父親事後得知女兒交了男友，請同居人的蔡姓女兒關心她，竟在少女手機內發現她傳了「插進去的時候會痛，今天上學有不舒服。」給鄭男，蔡女驚訝之下連忙問少女對方有無做安全措施，並將事情告訴少女父親。<br />\n<br />\n少女父親事後憤而報警，然而鄭男開庭時卻矢口否認2人有發生關係，僅承認有相互擁吻。此外，鄭男還在事發後與少女互道思念，「我好想妳」、「依然愛妳」、「對的人值得等待，即使距離很遠，但是心不遠」等，且還要求對方刪除對話紀錄，而少女也甜蜜回應。<br />\n<br />\n對此，新北地院認為，鄭男明知少女年僅12歲，卻未控制自身私欲而與對方發生關係，還矢口否認犯行，甚至要求對方刪除對話，並且為了自保還要對方與自己口徑一致，因此認定他難有悔意，將他判處3年6個月有期徒刑。全案可上訴。"},{"pid":"8a83a20d1b9a0d3d14cffb45597d996f8e2e4691","tid":1079540,"uid":136038,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"點先可以移民台灣新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116a5a3251a7d572fb3f5e15ba0eb387baf65899","tid":1079540,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"並與母親所雇用的12歲少女交往<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來台灣可以請童工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb995b9bcdac7c004fc656fedabd52ca418910a","tid":1079540,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"所......"},{"pid":"594af14f8ed1bcc0fd07563cac07ee25c806f55e","tid":1079540,"uid":199074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"12歲一定好窄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea96bfe9624ed13e22750400a8d2ffddd86325ae","tid":1079540,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"116a5a3251a7d572fb3f5e15ba0eb387baf65899","tid":1079540,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"並與母親所雇用的12歲少女交往<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來台灣可以請童工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"包服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c296dc757b681ca48307b5f53caa835f540cd065","tid":1079540,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"又中地方"},{"pid":"20cebd7a879d323ddf6d661c35156b660de1df2c","tid":1079540,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"594af14f8ed1bcc0fd07563cac07ee25c806f55e","tid":1079540,"uid":199074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"12歲一定好窄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"供詞有冇寫要吐口水先插入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aaa1422f9944f333a3e02b97eeb0d6090dcda2","tid":1079540,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"594af14f8ed1bcc0fd07563cac07ee25c806f55e","tid":1079540,"uid":199074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"12歲一定好窄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08099a02856d5823956cafa8932e81ae76a04b6f","tid":1079540,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594af14f8ed1bcc0fd07563cac07ee25c806f55e","tid":1079540,"uid":199074,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"12歲一定